==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''gutless wonder'''
#(slang) A sarcastic term for someone who lacks [[guts]] (courage); a [[coward]].
:''"Yer can't even fight unless you've got a knife or picket or broken bottle, yer '''gutless wonder'''."'' - ''Going Home'' by Archie Weller - (1993) [http://books.google.com/books?ie=UTF-8&vid=ISBN0044423160&id=50j03Q-5UhcC&q=%22gutless+wonder%22&dq=%22gutless+wonder%22]
